#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:4
msgid "The Mozilla Manifesto"
msgstr "Maniffesto Mozilla"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:8
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Cyflwyniad"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:12
msgid "The Internet is becoming an increasingly important part of our lives."
msgstr "Mae'r Rhyngrwyd yn dod yn rhan gynyddol bwysig o'n bywydau."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:16
msgid ""
"The Mozilla project is a global community of people who believe that "
"openness, innovation, and opportunity are key to the continued health of the "
"Internet. We have worked together since 1998 to ensure that the Internet is "
"developed in a way that benefits everyone. We are best known for creating "
"the Mozilla Firefox web browser."
msgstr ""
"Mae prosiect Mozilla yn gymuned fyd-eang o bobl sy'n credu bod bod yn "
"agored, arloesedd, a chyfle yn allweddol i iechyd parhaus y Rhyngrwyd. Rydym "
"wedi gweithio gyda'i gilydd ers 1998 i sicrhau fod y Rhyngrwyd yn cael ei "
"ddatblygu mewn ffordd sydd o fudd i bawb. Rydym yn fwyaf adnabyddus am "
"greu'r porwr gwe Mozilla Firefox."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:20
msgid ""
"The Mozilla project uses a community-based approach to create world-class "
"open source software and to develop new types of collaborative activities. "
"We create communities of people involved in making the Internet experience "
"better for all of us."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r prosiect Mozilla yn defnyddio dull sy'n seiliedig ar y gymuned i greu "
"meddalwedd cod agored byd-eang ac i ddatblygu mathau newydd o weithgareddau "
"cydweithredol. Rydym yn creu cymunedau o bobl sy'n gysylltiedig â gwneud "
"profiad y Rhyngrwyd yn well i bob un ohonom."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:24
msgid ""
"As a result of these efforts, we have distilled a set of principles that we "
"believe are critical for the Internet to continue to benefit the public good "
"as well as commercial aspects of life. We set out these principles below."
msgstr ""
"O ganlyniad i'r ymdrechion hyn, rydym wedi distyllu set o egwyddorion y "
"credwn eu bod yn hanfodol ar gyfer y Rhyngrwyd i barhau i gynnig budd i'r "
"cyhoedd yn ogystal ag agweddau masnachol ar fywyd. Rydym yn gosod allan yr "
"egwyddorion hyn isod."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:28
msgid "The goals for the Manifesto are to:"
msgstr "Y nodau ar gyfer y Maniffesto yw i:"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:32
msgid ""
"articulate a vision for the Internet that Mozilla participants want the "
"Mozilla Foundation to pursue;"
msgstr ""
"mynegi gweledigaeth ar gyfer y Rhyngrwyd y mae cyfranwyr Mozilla am i'r "
"Mozilla Foundation ei ddilyn;"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:36
msgid "speak to people whether or not they have a technical background;"
msgstr "siarad â phobl os oes ganddynt gefndir technegol neu beidio;"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:40
msgid ""
"make Mozilla contributors proud of what we're doing and motivate us to "
"continue; and"
msgstr ""
"gwneud cyfranwyr Mozilla yn falch o'r hyn rydym yn ei wneud a'n hannog ni i "
"barhau; a"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:44
msgid ""
"provide a framework for other people to advance this vision of the Internet."
msgstr "darparu fframwaith i bobl eraill hybu y weledigaeth hon o'r Rhyngrwyd."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:48
msgid ""
"These principles will not come to life on their own. People are needed to "
"make the Internet open and participatory - people acting as individuals, "
"working together in groups, and leading others. The Mozilla Foundation is "
"committed to advancing the principles set out in the Mozilla Manifesto. We "
"invite others to join us and make the Internet an ever better place for "
"everyone."
msgstr ""
"Ni fydd yr egwyddorion hyn yn dod yn fyw ar eu pen eu hunain. Mae angen pobl "
"i wneud y Rhyngrwyd yn agored ac yn gyfranogol - pobl sy'n gweithredu fel "
"unigolion, yn gweithio gyda'i gilydd mewn grwpiau, ac arwain eraill. Mae'r "
"Mozilla Foundation yn ymrwymedig i hyrwyddo egwyddorion a nodir ym "
"Maniffesto Mozilla. Rydym yn gwahodd eraill i ymuno â ni a gwneud y "
"Rhyngrwyd yn lle gwell byth i bawb."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:52
msgid "Principles"
msgstr "Egwyddorion"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:56
msgid ""
"The Internet is an integral part of modern life—a key component in "
"education, communication, collaboration, business, entertainment and society "
"as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r Rhyngrwyd yn rhan annatod o fywyd modern—yn elfen allweddol mewn "
"addysg, cyfathrebu, cydweithredu, busnes, adloniant a chymdeithas yn "
"gyffredinol."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:60
msgid ""
"The Internet is a global public resource that must remain open and "
"accessible."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r Rhyngrwyd yn adnodd cyhoeddus byd-eang y mae'n rhaid iddo aros yn "
"agored ac yn hygyrch."

#. Old string, will be removed after bug 876814 is fixed
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:65
msgid "The Internet should enrich the lives of individual human beings."
msgstr "Dylai'r Rhyngrwyd gyfoethogi bywydau bodau dynol unigol."

#. New string for bug 876814
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:70
msgid "The Internet must enrich the lives of individual human beings."
msgstr "Rhaid i'r Rhyngrwyd gyfoethogi bywydau bodau dynol unigol."

#. Old string, will be removed after bug 876814 is fixed
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:75
msgid ""
"Individuals’ security on the Internet is fundamental and cannot be treated "
"as optional."
msgstr ""
"Mae diogelwch unigolion ar y Rhyngrwyd yn fater sylfaenol ac nid oes modd ei "
"drin fel dewisol."

#. New string for bug 876814
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:80
msgid ""
"Individuals’ security and privacy on the Internet are fundamental and must "
"not be treated as optional."
msgstr ""
"Mae diogelwch unigolion ar y Rhyngrwyd yn fater sylfaenol ac nid oes modd ei "
"drin fel mater dewisol."

#. Old string, will be removed after bug 876814 is fixed
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:85
msgid ""
"Individuals must have the ability to shape their own experiences on the "
"Internet."
msgstr ""
"Rhaid i unigolion gael y gallu i lunio eu profiadau eu hunain ar y Rhyngrwyd."

#. New string for bug 876814
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:90
msgid ""
"Individuals must have the ability to shape the Internet and their own "
"experiences on the Internet."
msgstr ""
"Rhaid i unigolion gael y gallu i lunio'r Rhyngrwyd a'u profiadau eu hunain "
"ar y Rhyngrwyd."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:94
msgid ""
"The effectiveness of the Internet as a public resource depends upon "
"interoperability (protocols, data formats, content), innovation and "
"decentralized participation worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Mae effeithiolrwydd y Rhyngrwyd fel adnodd cyhoeddus yn dibynnu ar y gallu i "
"ryngweithredu (protocolau, fformatau data, cynnwys), arloesi a chyfranogiad "
"datganoledig ledled y byd."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:98
msgid ""
"Free and open source software promotes the development of the Internet as a "
"public resource."
msgstr ""
"Mae meddalwedd cod agored ac am ddim yn hyrwyddo datblygiad y Rhyngrwyd fel "
"adnodd cyhoeddus."

#. Old string, will be removed after bug 876814 is fixed
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:103
msgid ""
"Transparent community-based processes promote participation, accountability, "
"and trust."
msgstr ""
"Mae prosesau tryloyw cymunedol yn hyrwyddo cyfranogiad, atebolrwydd, ac "
"ymddiriedaeth."

#. New string for bug 876814
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:108
msgid ""
"Transparent community-based processes promote participation, accountability "
"and trust."
msgstr ""
"Mae prosesau tryloyw cymunedol yn hyrwyddo cyfranogiad, atebolrwydd, ac "
"ymddiriedaeth."

#. Old string, will be removed after bug 876814 is fixed
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:113
msgid ""
"Commercial involvement in the development of the Internet brings many "
"benefits; a balance between commercial goals and public benefit is critical."
msgstr ""
"Mae cyfranogiad masnachol yn natblygiad y Rhyngrwyd yn dod â llawer o "
"fuddion; mae cydbwysedd rhwng nodau masnachol a budd cyhoeddus yn hanfodol."

#. New string for bug 876814
#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:118
msgid ""
"Commercial involvement in the development of the Internet brings many "
"benefits; a balance between commercial profit and public benefit is critical."
msgstr ""
"Mae cyfranogiad masnachol yn natblygiad y Rhyngrwyd yn dod â llawer o "
"fuddion; mae cael cydbwysedd rhwng elw masnachol a budd cyhoeddus yn "
"hanfodol."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:122
msgid ""
"Magnifying the public benefit aspects of the Internet is an important goal, "
"worthy of time, attention and commitment."
msgstr ""
"Mae cynyddu agweddau budd cyhoeddus y Rhyngrwyd yn nod pwysig, teilwng o'n "
"hamser, sylw ac ymrwymiad."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:126
msgid "Advancing the Mozilla Manifesto"
msgstr "Hyrwyddo Maniffesto Mozilla"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:130
msgid ""
"There are many different ways of advancing the principles of the Mozilla "
"Manifesto. We welcome a broad range of activities, and anticipate the same "
"creativity that Mozilla participants have shown in other areas of the "
"project. For individuals not deeply involved in the Mozilla project, one "
"basic and very effective way to support the Manifesto is to use Mozilla "
"Firefox and other products that embody the principles of the Manifesto."
msgstr ""
"Mae llawer o wahanol ffyrdd o hyrwyddo egwyddorion Maniffesto Mozilla. Rydym "
"yn croesawu ystod eang o weithgareddau, ac yn rhagweld yr un creadigrwydd y "
"mae cyfranogwyr Mozilla wedi eu hamlygu mewn meysydd eraill yn y prosiect. "
"Ar gyfer unigolion nad ydynt yn ymwneud yn fawr â phrosiect Mozilla, y "
"ffordd amlwg ac effeithiol iawn i gefnogi'r Maniffesto yw drwy ddefnyddio "
"Mozilla Firefox a chynnyrch eraill sy'n ymgorffori egwyddorion y Maniffesto."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:134
msgid "Mozilla Foundation Pledge"
msgstr "Addewid y Mozilla Foundation"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:138
msgid ""
"The Mozilla Foundation pledges to support the Mozilla Manifesto in its "
"activities. Specifically, we will:"
msgstr ""
"Mae Mozilla Foundation yn addo i gefnogi Maniffesto Mozilla yn ei "
"weithgareddau. Yn benodol, byddwn yn:"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:142
msgid ""
"build and enable open-source technologies and communities that support the "
"Manifesto’s principles;"
msgstr ""
"adeiladu a galluogi technolegau a chymunedau cod agored sy'n cefnogi "
"egwyddorion y Maniffesto;"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:146
msgid ""
"build and deliver great consumer products that support the Manifesto’s "
"principles;"
msgstr ""
"adeiladu a chyflwyno cynnyrch gwych i ddefnyddwyr sy'n cefnogi egwyddorion y "
"Maniffesto;"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:150
msgid ""
"use the Mozilla assets (intellectual property such as copyrights and "
"trademarks, infrastructure, funds, and reputation) to keep the Internet an "
"open platform;"
msgstr ""
"ddefnyddio asedau Mozilla (eiddo deallusol megis hawlfraint a nodau masnach, "
"seilwaith, cronfeydd, ac enw da) i gadw'r Rhyngrwyd yn llwyfan agored;"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:154
msgid "promote models for creating economic value for the public benefit; and"
msgstr "hyrwyddo modelau ar gyfer creu gwerth economaidd er budd y cyhoedd, a"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:158
msgid ""
"promote the Mozilla Manifesto principles in public discourse and within the "
"Internet industry."
msgstr ""
"hyrwyddo egwyddorion Maniffesto Mozilla mewn trafodaethau cyhoeddus ac o "
"fewn diwydiant y Rhyngrwyd."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:162
msgid ""
"Some Foundation activities—currently the creation, delivery and promotion of "
"consumer products—are conducted primarily through the Mozilla Foundation’s "
"wholly owned subsidiary, the Mozilla Corporation."
msgstr ""
"Mae rhai o weithgareddau'r Foundation — sef, ar hyn o bryd, creu, cyflwyno a "
"hyrwyddo cynnyrch defnyddwyr yn cael eu cynnal yn bennaf drwy'r Mozilla "
"Corporation, is-gwmni sy'n eiddo i'r Mozilla Foundation."

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:166
msgid "Invitation"
msgstr "Gwahoddiad"

#: mozorg/about/manifesto.lang:170
msgid ""
"The Mozilla Foundation invites all others who support the principles of the "
"Mozilla Manifesto to join with us, and to find new ways to make this vision "
"of the Internet a reality."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r Mozilla Foundation yn gwahodd pawb arall sy'n cefnogi egwyddorion "
"Maniffesto Mozilla i ymuno gyda ni, ac i ddod o hyd i ffyrdd newydd i wneud "
"y weledigaeth hon o'r Rhyngrwyd yn fyw."
